  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this randomized study the investigators wish to explore the role of pre-procedural statin
      therapy for the prevention of contrast induced nephropathy in patients with
      moderate-to-severe renal dysfunction, submitted to elective coronary or angioplasty.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
